## Stack & Tools

| Layer | Tech |
|---|---|
| Frontend | React 18 + TypeScript (strict), Vite 5 |
| Blockchain | Viem 2, Arc Testnet (EVM-compatible) |
| Contracts | Hardhat + Solidity, V5 prediction market |
| Wallet | EIP-6963 discovery, WalletConnect, Magic.link (email) |
| Cross-chain | LI.FI SDK, Circle App Kit (USDC swaps) |
| Indexer | Node.js custom indexer (`indexer/server.mjs`) |
| Oracle | AI resolution (Gemini/OpenAI) + on-chain adapters |
| Testing | Hardhat (unit), Playwright (e2e) |

